    "description": "Complete API collection for testing EpesiCRM multi-tenant application\n\nüöÄ QUICK START GUIDE:\n\n1. First, run 'Register New User' - this will automatically save your accessToken and tenantId\n2. The collection will auto-populate {{accessToken}} and {{tenantId}} variables\n3. Now you can test any protected endpoint!\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT TIPS:\n\n- Access tokens expire in 15 minutes - just register a new user or use the refresh endpoint\n- Always create parent resources first (e.g., Company before Contact with companyId)\n- Use {{$timestamp}} in emails/usernames to avoid duplicates\n- Foreign key errors? Create the referenced resource first or omit the ID field\n\nüìã PROPER ORDER FOR RELATED RESOURCES:\n\n1. Create Company ‚Üí then create Contact with that companyId\n2. Create Contact ‚Üí then create Deal with that contactId\n3. Create Product ‚Üí then create Deal with that productId\n\nThe collection variables will save IDs automatically as you create resources!",
